---
import ArrowLeft from "../../assets/icons/ArrowLeft.astro";
---

<div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-20">
  <div class="w-full h-full xl:max-w-[75%] px-10 sm:px-20">
    <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-start justify-center gap-8">
      <div
        class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 text-center"
      >
        <p
          data-reveal
          class="text-sm sm:text-base font-light text-white uppercase"
        >
          ¿QUIÉNES SOMOS?
        </p>

        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="80" class="w-full bg-white px-5 py-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-black drop-shadow">
            Un equipo pequeño, enfocado y complementario
          </h2>
        </div>

        <p data-reveal data-reveal-delay="160" class="text-sm sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white drop-shadow">
          Combinamos visión técnica y enfoque de negocio para desarrollar
          soluciones que no solo funcionan, sino que tienen sentido en el
          contexto de cada proyecto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="w-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-4"
      >
        <!-- ENGINEERING FLIP CARD -->
        <div
          data-reveal
          data-reveal-delay="80"
          class="flip-container w-full grow"
          style="perspective: 1200px; min-height: 420px;"
        >
          <div
            class="flip-inner w-full h-full"
            style="position: relative; transform-style: preserve-3d; transition: transform 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.4,0.2,0.2,1);"
            data-flipped="false"
          >
            <!-- FRONT: Engineering role -->
            <div
              class="flip-face w-full h-full flex flex-col items-start justify-between bg-black shadow-lg gap-4 px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer group"
              style="backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; position: absolute; inset: 0;"
              onclick="this.closest('.flip-inner').classList.add('is-flipped'); this.closest('.flip-inner').dataset.flipped='true'"
            >
              <div class="w-full">
                <div class="w-full shadow-lg py-4 transition-all duration-500">
                  <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-secondary uppercase">
                    INGENIERÍA
                  </h3>
                  <h4 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-light text-secondary uppercase">
                    Desarrollo y arquitectura técnica
                  </h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-base text-white">
                Encargado de diseñar y construir la base técnica de cada proyecto.
                Desde páginas web hasta automatización de procesos, el enfoque está
                en crear soluciones estables, rápidas y bien estructuradas.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-3 w-full">
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Eficiencia y rendimiento
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Soluciones escalables
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Implementaciones limpias y mantenibles
                </p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary/60 font-light self-end flex items-center gap-1 mt-2">
                <span>Ver equipo</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/></svg>
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- BACK: Mauricio -->
            <div
              class="flip-face w-full h-full flex flex-col items-start justify-between bg-black border border-secondary/40 shadow-lg gap-4 px-5 py-4"
              style="backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; transform: rotateY(180deg); position: absolute; inset: 0;"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between w-full">
                <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
                  <img
                    src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4D03AQETLSMaC7f-WQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1649435378295?e=1781136000&v=beta&t=qTf2eVJVt1mqM_kdQUwGDo46txUF7Dx-baWlL2XlAE0"
                    alt="Mauricio Garzón Brunal"
                    class="w-14 h-14 object-cover shrink-0 ring-2 ring-secondary/50"
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight">
                      Mauricio Garzón Brunal
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-light text-secondary uppercase tracking-wide">
                      Full-Stack &amp; RN Developer
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button
                  class="text-white/30 hover:text-white/80 transition-colors duration-200 shrink-0 ml-2 cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="this.closest('.flip-inner').classList.remove('is-flipped'); this.closest('.flip-inner').dataset.flipped='false'"
                  aria-label="Volver"
                >
                  <div class="w-10 h-10"><ArrowLeft color="currentColor" /></div>
                </button>
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline gap-2 border-l-2 border-secondary pl-3">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary leading-none">+6</span>
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                  <span class="text-xs text-white font-semibold leading-tight">años de experiencia</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-white/50 font-light">Ing. Sistemas · Univ. de Medellín 2023</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="text-sm font-light text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
                Desarrolla aplicaciones web y móviles full-stack — backend con Express
                y NestJS, bases de datos SQL y NoSQL, frontend con React, React Native
                y Vue.js. Trayectoria en equipos de producto desde 2019.
              </p>

              <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">TypeScript</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">React / RN</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">NestJS</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">AWS</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">GraphQL</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full">Vue.js</span>
              </div>

              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maugarbru/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-xs text-secondary font-light hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 no-underline"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path d="M20.5 2h-17A1.5 1.5 0 002 3.5v17A1.5 1.5 0 003.5 22h17a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5v-17A1.5 1.5 0 0020.5 2zM8 19H5v-9h3zM6.5 8.25A1.75 1.75 0 118.3 6.5a1.78 1.78 0 01-1.8 1.75zM19 19h-3v-4.74c0-1.42-.6-1.93-1.38-1.93A1.74 1.74 0 0013 14.19a.66.66 0 000 .14V19h-3v-9h2.9v1.3a3.11 3.11 0 012.7-1.4c1.55 0 3.36.86 3.36 3.66z"/>
                </svg>
                linkedin.com/in/maugarbru
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BUSINESS FLIP CARD -->
        <div
          data-reveal
          data-reveal-delay="180"
          class="flip-container w-full grow"
          style="perspective: 1200px; min-height: 420px;"
        >
          <div
            class="flip-inner w-full h-full"
            style="position: relative; transform-style: preserve-3d; transition: transform 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.4,0.2,0.2,1);"
            data-flipped="false"
          >
            <!-- FRONT: Business role -->
            <div
              class="flip-face w-full h-full flex flex-col items-start justify-between bg-black shadow-lg gap-4 px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer group"
              style="backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; position: absolute; inset: 0;"
              onclick="this.closest('.flip-inner').classList.add('is-flipped'); this.closest('.flip-inner').dataset.flipped='true'"
            >
              <div class="w-full">
                <div class="w-full shadow-lg py-4 transition-all duration-500">
                  <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-tertiary uppercase">
                    Negocio / Producto
                  </h3>
                  <h4 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-light text-tertiary uppercase">
                    Estrategia y enfoque de producto
                  </h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-base text-white">
                Encargada de entender el negocio, estructurar la experiencia del
                usuario y asegurar que cada solución tenga un objetivo claro. Desde
                la definición hasta la validación, todo se construye con sentido
                práctico.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-3 w-full">
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Claridad en la propuesta
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Experiencia del usuario
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white font-light drop-shadow p-2 bg-primary/50 rounded-full">
                  Enfoque en resultados reales
                </p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-tertiary/60 font-light self-end flex items-center gap-1 mt-2">
                <span>Ver equipo</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/></svg>
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- BACK: Laura -->
            <div
              class="flip-face w-full h-full flex flex-col items-start justify-between bg-black border border-tertiary/40 shadow-lg gap-4 px-5 py-4"
              style="backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; transform: rotateY(180deg); position: absolute; inset: 0;"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between w-full">
                <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
                  <img
                    src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFShaoaYP2EKA/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1695070950850?e=1781136000&v=beta&t=bznky4fk8lbpFkioWYAUlGy_TDEs0CnllhnIlLkotRQ"
                    alt="Laura Mestra Ruíz"
                    class="w-14 h-14 object-cover shrink-0 ring-2 ring-tertiary/50"
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight">
                      Laura Mestra Ruíz
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-light text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wide">
                      Project Manager · Scrum Master
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button
                  class="text-white/30 hover:text-white/80 transition-colors duration-200 shrink-0 ml-2 cursor-pointer"
                  onclick="this.closest('.flip-inner').classList.remove('is-flipped'); this.closest('.flip-inner').dataset.flipped='false'"
                  aria-label="Volver"
                >
                  <div class="w-10 h-10"><ArrowLeft color="currentColor" /></div>
                </button>
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline gap-2 border-l-2 border-tertiary pl-3">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-tertiary leading-none">+4</span>
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                  <span class="text-xs text-white font-semibold leading-tight">años de experiencia</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-white/50 font-light">Negocios Internacionales · Univ. de Medellín 2021</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="text-sm font-light text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
                Profesional en Negocios Internacionales y Scrum Master certificada.
                Gestiona proyectos de software con claridad de objetivos, liderazgo
                de equipos y metodologías ágiles desde 2021.
              </p>

              <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full">Project Management</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full">Scrum Master</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full">Agile</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full">Negocios Internacionales</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/60 px-2 py-1 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full">Stakeholders</span>
              </div>

              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lauramestraru/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-xs text-tertiary font-light hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 no-underline"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path d="M20.5 2h-17A1.5 1.5 0 002 3.5v17A1.5 1.5 0 003.5 22h17a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5v-17A1.5 1.5 0 0020.5 2zM8 19H5v-9h3zM6.5 8.25A1.75 1.75 0 118.3 6.5a1.78 1.78 0 01-1.8 1.75zM19 19h-3v-4.74c0-1.42-.6-1.93-1.38-1.93A1.74 1.74 0 0013 14.19a.66.66 0 000 .14V19h-3v-9h2.9v1.3a3.11 3.11 0 012.7-1.4c1.55 0 3.36.86 3.36 3.66z"/>
                </svg>
                linkedin.com/in/lauramestraru
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .flip-inner.is-flipped {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .flip-inner {
      transition: none !important;
    }
    .flip-inner.is-flipped {
      transform: none !important;
    }
    .flip-inner .flip-face:nth-child(2) {
      transform: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
    }
    .flip-inner.is-flipped .flip-face:nth-child(1) {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .flip-inner.is-flipped .flip-face:nth-child(2) {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
